1
00:00:10,096 --> 00:00:11,438
Dobro...

2
00:00:13,045 --> 00:00:14,387
Šta misliš sa "dobro"?

3
00:00:17,794 --> 00:00:19,277
Mislim, u redu je.

4
00:00:26,553 --> 00:00:28,259
Kada ceš ici da vidiš oca?

5
00:00:28,993 --> 00:00:30,580
Kasnije u kancelariju.

6
00:00:33,844 --> 00:00:34,922
Zašto?

7
00:00:36,543 --> 00:00:37,625
Samo pitam.

8
00:00:39,626 --> 00:00:43,286
<i>Sredinom decembra,
konacno sam dobio pismo od Eve.</i>

9
00:00:44,373 --> 00:00:47,678
<i>Njen otac 
joj je našao posao u gradu,</i>

10
00:00:47,713 --> 00:00:50,945
<i>koji ce zapoceti odmah
posle Nove godine.</i>

11
00:00:52,111 --> 00:00:55,394
<i>Od noci kada je došla
da potraži zaklon u školi,</i>

12
00:00:55,429 --> 00:00:57,494
<i>do svanuca,</i>

13
00:00:57,529 --> 00:01:01,142
<i>jedno drugome smo ispricali pricu
o našim kratkim životima,</i>

14
00:01:01,886 --> 00:01:03,379
<i>njeno bledo lice,</i>

15
00:01:03,414 --> 00:01:07,013
<i>njena stidljiva, ali otvorena licnost,</i>

16
00:01:07,602 --> 00:01:09,611
<i>mi je stalno bila na pameti.</i>

17
00:01:11,286 --> 00:01:14,854
<i>Školski raspust 
je trajao do drugog januara,</i>

18
00:01:15,491 --> 00:01:18,145
<i>ali vec
na dan posle Božica,</i>

19
00:01:18,180 --> 00:01:20,435
<i>po hladnom, ali suncem obasjanom danu,</i>

20
00:01:21,147 --> 00:01:22,865
<i>uputio sam se u Treglic</i>

21
00:01:22,900 --> 00:01:25,602
<i>da posetim Evu i njene roditelje.</i>

22
00:01:26,309 --> 00:01:27,447
A Sigi?

23
00:01:29,262 --> 00:01:32,053
Ne znam.
Bronesa se još uvek nije vratila.

24
00:01:36,138 --> 00:01:37,338
A Baron?

25
00:01:39,391 --> 00:01:42,360
Jedva da ga vidjamo.
Ne prica n isa kim.

26
00:01:46,580 --> 00:01:49,645
Ne znam.
Neki kažu da su otišli u Italiju.

27
00:01:49,745 --> 00:01:50,972
U Italiju?

